OL,3,CJudgment 'before Easter' in trial of
OL,4,Cdouble sectarian murder accused
OL,6,FJudgment in a trial concerning a man
OL,7,Faccused of the double sectarian
OL,8,Fmurders of two Catholic workmen in
OL,9,FBelfast in May 1994 will be made
OL,10,F"before Easter", a court heard today.
OL,12,FAfter closing submissions were made by
OL,13,Fthe Crown and defence, Mr Justice
OL,14,FO'Hara revealed he will give his
OL,15,Fruling on whether or not 57-year old
OL,16,FJames Stewart Smyth committed the
OL,17,Fmurders.
