OL,3,CJudgment 'before Easter' in trial of
OL,4,Cdouble sectarian murder accused
OL,6,FEamon Fox (41) and 24-year old Gary
OL,7,FConvie were working on a building site
OL,8,Fin the Tiger's Bay area of Belfast and
OL,9,Fwere sitting in a Vauxhall Polo eating
OL,10,Flunch when the car was riddled with
OL,11,Fbullets fired from a gunman standing
OL,12,Fin an adjacent children's playground.
OL,14,FThe attack was claimed by the UVF and
OL,15,Fit's Crown's case that Smyth - a
OL,16,Fformer member of the UDR from
OL,17,FForthriver Link in north Belfast - was
OL,18,Fthe gunman.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G2/10
