OL,3,CJudgment 'before Easter' in trial of
OL,4,Cdouble sectarian murder accused
OL,6,FAs well as denying the murders of Mr
OL,7,FConvie and Mr Fox, Smyth has also
OL,8,Fdenied the attempted murder of a third
OL,9,Fworkman on the same date.
OL,11,FHe has also denied possessing a Sten
OL,12,Fsub machine gun and a quantity of
OL,13,Fammunition with intent, and of being a
OL,14,Fmember of the UVF.
OL,16,FDuring a non-jury trial that was
OL,17,Fopened at Belfast Crown Court last
OL,18,FOctober, the Crown called a number of
OL,19,Fwitnesses including former UVF
OL,20,Fcommander turned supergrass Gary
OL,21,FHaggarty.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G3/10
