OL,6,FFrom the witness box, he implicated
OL,7,FSmyth as the gunman and said the
OL,8,Fworkmen were murdered due to "pure
OL,9,Fsectarianism."
OL,11,FDuring today's hearing, Haggarty's
OL,12,Freliability was questioned by defence
OL,13,Fbarrister Michael Borrelli KC who
OL,14,Fbranded Haggarty "a dangerous witness"
OL,15,Fand a "liar."
OL,17,FFirst to address the senior judge was
OL,18,FKieran Murphy KC who highlighted three
OL,19,F"substantial parts of the case".
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G4/10
