OL,6,FThese, he said, were Smyth's DNA
OL,7,Flocated on the collar of a jacket
OL,8,Ffound along with the murder weapon 11
OL,9,Fdays after the shooting; Smyth's
OL,10,Fprevious "bad character" of
OL,11,Finvolvement in a sectarian murder in
OL,12,FBallymena in January 1994 and
OL,13,FHaggarty's evidence.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G5/10
