OL,3,CJudgment 'before Easter' in trial of
OL,4,Cdouble sectarian murder accused
OL,6,FHe said the defence had made
OL,7,F"concessions" regarding Smyth being on
OL,8,Fthe run and in the company of Haggarty
OL,9,Fand others in the UVF around May 1994
OL,10,F- but it has never been proven how or
OL,11,Fwhen Smyth's DNA came to be on the
OL,12,Fjacket.
OL,14,FRegarding Haggarty, Mr Borrelli
OL,15,Fdescribed him as a "dangerous witness"
OL,16,Fand a man motivated by revenge.
OL,18,FHe added: "The man is a liar, he is a
OL,19,Fdangerous liar. He spent years living
OL,20,Fa lie to his family, his friends, his
OL,21,Ffellow terrorists.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G8/10
